==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Sombre
<hw>Som"bre</hw> }</mhw>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<def>To make somber, or dark; to make shady.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sombre</ent>⟦br⟧
