HEADWORD: Sombre
<hw>Som"bre</hw> }</mhw>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>Gloom; obscurity; duskiness; somberness.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

